      "kind": "Entity",
      "preferredName": "Diagnostic Trouble Code",
      "description": "Diagnostic trouble codes or short DTCs are used inside ECUs to monitor failures. They were introduced for measuring vehicle emissions. Major DTCs for emissions are standardized by ISO standard ISO 15031-6:2015 - so called OBD2 standard. Over time DTCs were also introduced in other ECUs also besides engine and emission control. Many DTCs are vehicle manufacturer specific. "
